[color=#ff0000][size=4]
REQUIREMENT:[/size][/color]

-NLA ESP ONLY/PLUGIN ONLY

[color=#ffff00][size=4]HOW TO INSTALL:[/size][/color]

1.Install NLA(plugin only/esp only)
2.Set your in game brightness to a center (50%)
3.Copy the main file to your skyrim folder, where the TESV.exe
4.(OPTIONAL)for no letterbox+vignette copy the file inside "no letterbox+vignette" to skyrim folder, where the TESV.exe
5.(OPTIONAL)for using gameplay DOF copy the file from the gameplay folder and for using photograph DOF copy the file from the photograph folder to skyrim folder
6.Enjoy your game
